msgid ""
"Beware of those orcs crossing the river! If they get into the forest they’ll "
"be hard to dislodge!"
msgstr ""
"Čuvaj se tih orkova što prelaze reku! Uđu li u šumu, biće ih teško izglaviti "
"odande!"

